Assignment 1.08 for Coms 327
Made by Trevor Luster using code from Jeremy Shaeffer
2017-03-30

Implements monster and item generation from a monster_desc.txt 
file and object_desc.txt file respectively. Both files must be 
found in $HOME/.rlg327 or else the program will crash. Also
implements rendering the instance's given color in ncurses.


Compile command:
	make rlg327

Run command:
	./rlg327

Clean command:
	make clean